                    <div class="article-main">
                        <div class="article-intro">
                            <p class="lead">Discovering your IT provider holds your Microsoft licences hostage is every Canadian business owner's nightmare. You're locked into expensive contracts, trapped with poor service, and facing thousands in "migration fees" to escape. This comprehensive guide shows you how to regain control of your Microsoft 365, Azure, and CSP licences across Canada.</p>
