                            <p>Don't let another month pass paying inflated fees or accepting poor service because you feel trapped. Take action today to assess your situation and explore your options for regaining Microsoft licensing freedom.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="cta-box">
                            <h3>Need Help Escaping Your Microsoft Licensing Hostage Situation?</h3>
